channel.title: Defyboys Cache Extractor
channel.description:
Hey everyone :|
** I also posted this in the Questions section, no one replied though.. **
i'm having trouble getting a .mdl file, all the things i have are .dat, i thought it was something to do with defyboys cache extractor.. :o
but for some weird reason i can't seem to get it, so if someone could waste 1 minute of there time uploading it for me, i would be forever grateful.
(you may or may not be wondering why i want a .mdl file, well, it's so i can use Gzip to turn it into a .gz file so then i can add it to my client)
(you may also be wondering how i got the .dat models, well it was quite simple actually, i just downloaded that runescape model viewer by bentski and then clicked on the run.bat thing. then i waited about 1 or 2 hours for the 40k .dat files to be placed on my comp.)
thanks in advance. :cool:
